headline: GlobalFoundries Appoints Vincent Feng as Vice President of Sales for Asia Pacific
summary: GlobalFoundries (NASDAQ: GFS) (GF) today announced the appointment of industry veteran Vincent Feng as Vice President of Sales for Asia Pacific (APAC). With more than 25 years of semiconductor industry experience, Mr. Feng will lead GF's sales and customer engagements across the Taiwan region, South Korea, Japan, Singapore and India.
